								<h3 class="box-title">Privacy</h3>
							</div>
							<div class="box-body">
								<p>
									We pledge to NEVER distribute or sell any of your identifying information.  
									Any studies which use the datasets that we cultivate will adhere to the strictest set of anonymity guidelines possible.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
		
					<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
						<div class="box box-solid">
							<div class="box-header bg-light-blue">
								<i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
								<h3 class="box-title">Born in Boston</h3>
							</div>
							<div class="box-body">
								<p>
									CalcU is a simple idea that was started at Brandeis University in Boston. It was made by an optimistic undergrad with the sole goal of making
									learning calculus easier. To get involved in the project, or to contribute commentary or feedback, please reach out by checking out our contact page.
								</p>
							</div>
